      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·邶風·003.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">燕燕.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>燕燕于飛，下上其音，之子于歸，遠送于南，瞻望弗及，實勞我心。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The swallows go flying about;
From below, from above, comes their twittering.
The lady was returning to her native state,
And far did I escort her to the south.
I looked till I could no longer see her,
And great was the grief of my heart.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
