      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·邶風·003.4</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">燕燕.4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>仲氏任只，其心塞淵，終溫且惠，淑慎其身，先君之思，以勗寡人。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Lovingly confiding was the lady Chung;
Truly deep was her feeling.
Both gentle was she and docile,
Virtuously careful of her person.
In thinking of our deceased lord,
She stimulated worthless me.</seg>
      </tuv>
